summary: This collection of documents pertains to the Agency's interest in Luis Albert Ferre and Antonio Luis Ferre, including security approvals and discussions related to Project WUBRINY and Antilles Materials Company Limited (AMCO). It covers meetings with SKEWER/1, assessments of AMCO's commercial viability, and potential collaboration with the Puerto Rican Cement Company.
title: Project WUBRINY - Luis Albert Ferre and Antilles Materials Company Limited (AMCO)
